{"link_name": "Realizando Backup do Schema e do Banco de Dados do Zabbix", "type": "Integration", "OS": "General", "vendor": "Others", "minZabbVer": "4.0.x", "link_desc": "<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #24292e; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji'; font-size: 16px;\">Esse script realiza o backup do schema do banco bem como backup do banco do Zabbix mas ignorando as maiores tabelas.</p>\n<pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; overflow-wrap: normal; padding: 16px; overflow: auto; line-height: 1.45; background-color: #f6f8fa; border-radius: 3px; color: #24292e;\"><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background: initial; border-radius: 3px; word-break: normal; border: 0px; display: inline; overflow: visible; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: normal;\">yum install git gzip\n\ngit clone https://github.com/everaldoscabral/script_banco_zabbix.git\n\ncd script_banco_zabbix/\n\nchmod +x script_banco_zabbix.sh\n\n./script_banco_zabbix.sh\n</code></pre>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #24292e; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji'; font-size: 16px;\">Ap\u00f3s finalizar o processo de backup, caso queira testar o restore do schema e do banco:</p>\n<h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 2em; margin: 24px 0px 16px; line-height: 1.25; padding-bottom: 0.3em; border-bottom: 1px solid #eaecef; color: #24292e; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji';\"><a id=\"user-content-restaurando-o-schema-do-banco-do-zabbix\" class=\"anchor\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: #0366d6; float: left; padding-right: 4px; margin-left: -20px; line-height: 1;\" href=\"https://github.com/everaldoscabral/script_banco_zabbix#restaurando-o-schema-do-banco-do-zabbix\"></a>Restaurando o schema do banco do Zabbix</h1>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #24292e; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji'; font-size: 16px;\">sudo gunzip < ARQUIVO-schema.sql.gz | sudo mysql -u USUARIO -pSENHA BANCO_DE_RESTORE</p>\n<h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 2em; margin: 24px 0px 16px; line-height: 1.25; padding-bottom: 0.3em; border-bottom: 1px solid #eaecef; color: #24292e; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji';\"><a id=\"user-content-restaurando-o-banco-do-zabbix\" class=\"anchor\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: #0366d6; float: left; padding-right: 4px; margin-left: -20px; line-height: 1;\" href=\"https:", "features": "Custom Script", "address": "", "city": "", "state": "", "country": "", "postcode": "", "telephone": "", "fax": "", "email": "", "website": "http://everaldoscabral.blogspot.com/2020/04/sobre-zabbix-realizando-backup-do.html", "price": 0, "link_hits": 3595, "link_votes": 1, "link_rating": 5, "link_featured": null, "link_created": "2020-04-24 14:24:24", "link_modified": "0000-00-00 00:00:00", "link_visited": 282, "publish_up": "2020-04-24 14:24:24", "publish_down": "0000-00-00 00:00:00", "metakey": "", "metadesc": "", "1.8": "", "2.0": "", "2.2": "", "2.4": "", "3.0": "", "3.2": "", "3.4": "", "4.0": "", "4.2": "", "4.4": "", "5.0": "", "5.2": "", "tags": "MySQL, mysqldump, Zabbix, Zabbix Server, Backup", "author": "Everaldo Santos Cabral", "user_id": 11053, "link_id": 2067